trans-unit.source: Represents an entry in either back or forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Representa una entrada del historial de retroceso o de avance de navegación.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] implements a navigation history service that stores one entry for each piece of content that has been previously navigated to, just like navigation history in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementa un servicio de historial de navegación que almacena una entrada para cada parte del contenido que se ha navegado anteriormente, al igual que el historial de navegación en [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Navigation history comprises two stacks, one that remembers back navigation history, and one that remembers forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Historial de navegación consta de dos pilas, una que recuerda el historial de navegación hacia atrás y otra que recuerda el historial de navegación hacia delante.

trans-unit.source: An entry for the current item is added to back navigation history when a forward navigation occurs.
trans-unit.target: Se agrega una entrada para el elemento actual al historial de navegación de retroceso cuando tenga lugar la navegación hacia delante.

trans-unit.source: This occurs in the following situations:
trans-unit.target: Esto se produce en las situaciones siguientes:

trans-unit.source: The `Navigate` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>).
trans-unit.target: El `Navigate` se llama al método (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>).

trans-unit.source: The `GoForward` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>).
trans-unit.target: El `GoForward` se llama al método (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>).

trans-unit.source: The forward button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-ui-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: El botón Reenviar en el panel de navegación [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-ui-md.md)] que se muestra en el navegador actual ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).

trans-unit.source: Likewise, an entry for the current item is added to forward navigation history before a back navigation occurs, which happens when:
trans-unit.target: Del mismo modo, se agrega una entrada para el elemento actual en el historial de navegación hacia atrás antes de que se produce una navegación hacia atrás, lo que ocurre cuando:

trans-unit.source: The `GoBack` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>).
trans-unit.target: El `GoBack` se llama al método (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>).

trans-unit.source: The back button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-ui-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: El botón Atrás en el panel de navegación [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-ui-md.md)] que se muestra en el navegador actual ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).

trans-unit.source: Each entry in back and forward navigation history is an instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> class.
trans-unit.target: Cada entrada en la parte posterior y el historial de navegación hacia delante son una instancia de la <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> clase.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> object encapsulates information about a particular navigation, including a name for the entry (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>), whether the entry is kept alive (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) and the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content that is navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Cada <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> objeto encapsula información sobre una navegación concreta, incluido un nombre para la entrada (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>), si la entrada se mantiene activa (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) y la [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] para el contenido que se navega (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).

trans-unit.source: You can retrieve all the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> objects in back navigation history by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> properties.
trans-unit.target: Puede recuperar todos los <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> objetos de historial de navegación en la parte posterior enumerando el <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> propiedades.

trans-unit.source: For forward navigation history, you can retrieve all the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> objects by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> properties.
trans-unit.target: Para el historial de navegación hacia atrás, puede recuperar todos los <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> objetos enumerando el <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> propiedades.

trans-unit.source: If you need to remove the most recent <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> object from back navigation history, to prevent navigation to it, for example, you can call the `RemoveBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>), which removes the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> object and returns a reference to it.
trans-unit.target: Si tiene que quitar la última <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> objeto del historial de navegación hacia atrás, para evitar la navegación a él, por ejemplo, puede llamar a la `RemoveBackEntry` método (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>), que quita el <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> de objetos y devuelve una referencia a él.

trans-unit.source: You cannot add <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> objects to navigation history, however, because you can neither instantiate nor derive from <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry>, and because no type implements a member to do so.
trans-unit.target: No se puede agregar <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> objetos al historial de navegación, sin embargo, dado que se pueden crear instancias ni derivan de <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry>, y porque ningún tipo implementa un miembro para realizar esta acción.

trans-unit.source: However, you can add custom <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> objects to back navigation history by calling the `AddBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> adds the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object to an internally-created <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> object, which is then added to the back navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Sin embargo, puede agregar personalizada <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> objetos al historial de navegación de retroceso mediante una llamada a la `AddBackEntry` método (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> agrega la <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> internamente-crea un objeto <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> objeto, que, a continuación, se agrega al historial de navegación hacia atrás.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to retrieve the most recent <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> object from the back navigation stack to get the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A> property values.
trans-unit.target: En el ejemplo siguiente se muestra cómo recuperar la última <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> objeto de la pila de navegación hacia atrás para obtener la <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A> y <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A> valores de propiedad.
